nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 131 is the 109th issue of the magazine Star Wars Insider and the 39th published by Titan Magazines. It was released on January 31, 2012.

Star Wars Insider celebrates the release of Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace in 3-D! Insider looks at the appeal of the villains whose brief screen time translates into popularity; all-new fiction and Jar Jar Binks.
